name: question
description:
You wake up in the morning. 

You do not know why you woke up so early.

You go out. You take a photo at 5:43 to capture that moment with the beautiful sky and traversing clouds.

Clouds, yes, clouds are there but also something else.

You realize there is a bright object. It is not the sun. It is not the moon. It is none of the stars. What is that? That is a question.

Artistic value (if any) is in timing, in composition. 

No photo manipulation beyond cropping, and adjusting the tone, color & contrast.

It is what it is. A question. 

740 × 1030px
